  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380720/extras/1ba8b25b7716a48e08b0c0a95ecc98f8.avif?t=1669986596\" width=600 height=600 /></span><br><br>Two intergalactic freelancers, Jacob and Ethan, are on a routine travel through space delivering supplies to faraway galaxies. On their way back home they make one last stop to a small, remote planet. There they meet a group of researchers who are studying the planet and trying to figure out its mysterious history.<br><br>Not everything is quite as it seems, though.<br><br>Strange things start to happen and no-one really seems to know what is going on or who or what is behind everything. But one thing is sure, Jacob and Ethan can not leave.<br><br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    a story-driven non-combat adventure<br></li><li>    puzzles with varying difficulties<br></li><li>    over 50 maps to explore<br></li><li>    two playable characters</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380720/extras/1ba8b25b7716a48e08b0c0a95ecc98f8.avif?t=1669986596\" width=600 height=600 /></span><br><br>Two intergalactic freelancers, Jacob and Ethan, are on a routine travel through space delivering supplies to faraway galaxies. On their way back home they make one last stop to a small, remote planet. There they meet a group of researchers who are studying the planet and trying to figure out its mysterious history.<br><br>Not everything is quite as it seems, though.<br><br>Strange things start to happen and no-one really seems to know what is going on or who or what is behind everything. But one thing is sure, Jacob and Ethan can not leave.<br><br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    a story-driven non-combat adventure<br></li><li>    puzzles with varying difficulties<br></li><li>    over 50 maps to explore<br></li><li>    two playable characters</li></ul>",
